2026-05-14T01:50:47.5942474Z 22    <!--
2026-05-14T01:50:47.5943283Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-14T01:50:47.5944205Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-14T01:50:47.5945085Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-14T01:50:47.5946153Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-14T01:50:47.5947151Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-14T01:50:47.5948422Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-14T01:50:47.5959005Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-14T01:50:47.5960143Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-14T01:50:47.5961167Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-14T01:50:47.5962156Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-14T01:50:47.5962941Z 33    -->
